psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer

Class InteractionEnricherStatisticsWriter<I extends Interaction>

  • java.lang.Object
    • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.EnricherStatisticsWriter<I>
      • psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener.impl.writer.InteractionEnricherStatisticsWriter<I>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, EnricherListener<I>, InteractionEnricherListener<I>, AnnotationsChangeListener<I>, ChecksumsChangeListener<I>, IdentifiersChangeListener<I>, InteractionChangeListener<I>, XrefsChangeListener<I>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InteractionEvidenceEnricherStatisticsWriter, ModelledInteractionEnricherStatisticsWriter

    public class InteractionEnricherStatisticsWriter<I extends Interaction>
extends EnricherStatisticsWriter<I>
implements InteractionEnricherListener<I>
    A statistics logger which records changes made by the enricher. Each addition, removal or update is counted and, upon the completion of the enrichment of the object, is logged in either a file of successes or failures depending on the enrichmentStatus.
    Since:
    18/07/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
